%description
This Perl extention allows you to extract meta information from
various types of image files.  In this release the following file
formats are supported:

   JPEG (plain JFIF and Exif)
   PNG
   GIF
   PBM/PGM/PPM
   SVG
   XBM/XPM
   BMP/DIB/RLE

